    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "### Description\n\nThe tailwindcss configuration relies on a string that has a single quote: \n`local target = \"@import 'tailwindcss';\"`\n\nDue to this restriction files with the strings `@import \"tailwindcss\";` are not found and you get errors like: \n\n```\ntailwindcss: -32603 Request textDocument/completion failed with message: Cannot read properties of undefined (reading 'length')\n```\n\nIs there an easy fix to search for single and double quotes? \n\nThank you!\n\nhttps://github.com/neovim/nvim-lspconfig/blob/master/lsp/tailwindcss.lua",
    "closed_at": "2026-04-03T18:43:23Z",
